<subSubSection id="C36E6532FF91FFFC488D66532E48FBF6" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BCB36B9FF91FFFC488D66532E48FBF6" blockId="42.[151,1436,797,1146]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC488D66532A6FFBBD" bold="true" box="[151,269,1049,1074]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">REMARKS</emphasis>
: According to F. Pleijel (
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC4A30665029D0FBBE" box="[554,690,1050,1073]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">pers. comm.</emphasis>
), it is dubious whether the several colour polymorphic varieties of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D3AFF91FFFC491066742A04FBDA" box="[266,358,1086,1109]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" genus="Hesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Annelida" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC491066742A04FBDA" box="[266,358,1086,1109]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Hesione</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represent several or one species. This is also the case of 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D3AFF91FFFC4BF066742F18FBD9" box="[1002,1146,1085,1110]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" genus="Hesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC4BF066742F18FBD9" box="[1002,1146,1085,1110]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">H. splendida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D3AFF91FFFC4CAB66742BB0FBF5" authority="Risso, 1826" authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1826" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" genus="Hesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="pantherina">
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC4CAB66742E2DFBD9" box="[1201,1359,1085,1110]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">H. pantherina</emphasis>
Risso, 
<number id="3DBC249EFF91FFFC488D662B2BB0FBF5" box="[151,210,1121,1146]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" value="1826.0">1826</number>
</taxonomicName>
, and for this reason, all the records of the two species in the Adriatic Sea are listed as 
<taxonomicName id="4C744D3AFF91FFFC4C8E66282E41FBF5" box="[1172,1315,1121,1146]" class="Polychaeta" family="Hesionidae" genus="Hesione" kingdom="Animalia" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="splendida">
<emphasis id="B900EAABFF91FFFC4C8E66282E41FBF5" box="[1172,1315,1121,1146]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">H. splendida</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
